snippet.title: Truss Me! Now available for Android devices!
snippet.description:
Truss Me! is a FREE game designed by a Professor of Aerospace Engineering at a top US School so you can learn to design structures while having fun. Available for Android devices on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ScientificMonkeyLLC.TrussMe

Also available for iPad and iPhone on the App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/truss-me!/id732367282?ls=1&mt=8
